Package: gofigR
Type: Package
Title: Client for GoFigr.io
Version: 0.2.1
Authors@R: person(family="Pacula", given="Maciej", email="maciej@gofigr.io", role=c("cph", "cre", "aut"))
Description: This library integrates with your RMarkdown documents to automatically publish
  figures to the GoFigr.io service. Supports both 'knitr' and interactive 
  execution within RStudio.
